SQLStatement:
-- Elimina la tabla temporal si existe c_country2 
DROP TABLE IF EXISTS "adempiere"."c_country2" ;

-- Crea tabla temporal de codigos de tres digitos 
 CREATE TABLE "adempiere"."c_country2" (
  "countrycode" CHAR(2) NOT NULL, 
  "countrycode3" CHAR(3) NOT NULL, 
  "countryid" CHAR(3) NOT NULL, 
  "name" VARCHAR(60) NOT NULL, 
  "detalle1" VARCHAR(20), 
  "detalle2" VARCHAR(20), 
  "modificado" NUMERIC(1,0)
) WITHOUT OIDS;

-- Reemplaza el codigo de la region por defecto de todos los paises
update  adempiere.c_region
set c_community_id=(
select adempiere.c_community.c_community_id 
from  adempiere.c_community 
where c_region.c_country_id=c_community.c_country_id );
